metadata.name: CyberShrimp
metadata.description: The CyberShrimp is an art piece that represents the potential of blockchain and crypto. Its sleek, robotic body and intricate details symbolize the limitless possibilities of decentralized systems. As you gaze upon the CyberShrimp, let it inspire you to think beyond the limitations of today's technology and to imagine a decentralized future that is secure, transparent, and fair for all.
